    <br />

    
    <center><table class="itemDisplayTable">
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Title:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">ENVIRONMENTAL MONITORING IN BIOPHARMACEUTICAL INDUSTRY</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Authors:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">NARENDIRAN R</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Keywords:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">ENVIRONMENTAL MONITORING, BIOPHARMACEUTICAL INDUSTRY</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Issue Date:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">1-May-2008 </td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Publisher:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">SRM UNIVERSITY</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Series/Report no.:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">4114</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Abstract:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Environmental conditions to be maintained in critical and non critical regions of production unit should be monitored according to their specifications. Environmental monitoring is done by two methods namely viable monitoring and non-viable monitoring. Viable monitoring includes counting of colony forming units (CFU) and non-viable monitoring includes particle counting.
The air samples in critical and non critical regions of production unit are collected by exposing the Soybean Casein Digest Medium Plates (SCDA-90mm) and Replicate Organism Detection and Counting Plates (RODAC-55mm) to the air in respective regions of production unit. The collected air sample plates are incubated at two different temperatures viz., 25±2 C and 37±2 c for 5 days. The colony forming units are counted and compared with the standard specifications. If the conditions are under the specifications, there is no problem but when the conditions are beyond the standard specifications, then the productions is shut down and the cause for contamination is verified and precautions are taken to avoid the cause of contamination.</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">URI:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue"><a href="http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/2346">http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/2346</a></td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Appears in Collections:</td><td class="metadataFieldValue"><a href="/dspace/handle/123456789/2251">Biotech-2008</a><br/></td></tr>
</table></center><br/>
